atg.commerce.pricing
Class TaxPriceInfo

java.lang.Object
  atg.commerce.pricing.AmountInfo
      atg.commerce.pricing.TaxPriceInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class TaxPriceInfo
extends AmountInfo

Represents tax price information.

Properties:

  • shippingItemsTaxPriceInfos is a map of shipping group IDs to TaxPriceInfos that describe the prices of shipping groups.
  • cityTax is any city tax.
  • countyTax is any county tax.
  • stateTax is any state tax.
  • districtTax is any district or territory tax.
  • countryTax is any country tax.
